<br />

<h2 class="pen"><a rel="bookmark" href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/index.php?id=1069" title="Permanent link to this article">Life, the universe and everything</a></h2>

<div class="post">

<div class="entrytext">

	<p>&#8220;Hitchhiker&#8217;s Guide to the Galaxy&#8221; the movie is supposed to come out in the next month or so. I saw a preview and it looks like it&#8217;ll be fun, but already I have one major, major problem with it. Ford Prefect does not have an English accent. Oh well&#8230;</p>

	<p>I&#8217;m trying to get going on my major cataloging project&#8212;full MARC records on 10 volumes of the prof&#8217;s choosing. I&#8217;m getting there. I&#8217;m taking a few days off to work on the homework and to celebrate our 15th wedding anniversary coming up on Sunday.</p>

	<p>We got a fright from our electric company. We finally have our annex separated off on it its own meter and wiring so we had the electric company turn off the meter so the renter can put it in his own name. Well&#8230;. they turned off the electric to the building next door and it took them a day to figure out why.</p>

	<p>Apparently we have always been paying their electricity bill and they have been paying ours. The kicker&#8230; they now want us to pay the difference for the past year&#8230; to the figure of&#8230;. hold onto your chairs&#8230;. $1,295.</p>

	<p>It&#8217;s not our fault by any stretch. Apparently, the mix up came when the attorneys who owned our building split off the electric. They mixed up the meters at some point then and it wasn&#8217;t discovered until we worked on ours.</p>

	<p>I was feeling guilty for not having Darlene&#8217;s website updated in an eon, but was having a hard time getting my web design program working for some reason. So I chucked it all and redesigned it from scratch. Though I cheated a little bit. I used the same template I had designed for this blog and adjusted it a little for her website. So they&#8217;re twins for a little while, but in the future it&#8217;ll get more of it&#8217;s own flavor. Check out <a hre="http://www.mudcatpottery.com">Mudcat Pottery</a>.</p>

	<p>Today is the day I get my annual performance review. I hate those things, but I&#8217;ll suck it up and be a good camper. Tomorrow I start my mini-homework vacation and won&#8217;t have to think about work for a few days.</p>



 

<p class="postmetadata alt">

<small>This entry was posted on Mar 15 by <a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/index.php?author=E.G.+Yarnetsky">E.G. Yarnetsky</a>. You can skip to the end and leave a response using the comment form.</small></p>

</div>

</div>




	

	<p>

